"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?20/26/20903/abstract/2\">",
"      Margaglione M, Brancaccio V, Giuliani N, et al. Increased risk for venous thrombosis in carriers of the prothrombin G--&gt;A20210 gene variant. Ann Intern Med 1998; 129:89.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
